c: 5
v: 13
t: "Ke kaloku ngenxa yokwaphula kwabo uMnqophiso, Sabaqalekisa, Senza neentliziyo zabo zaqaqadeka. Baguqula amazwi endaweni yawo (yemfanelo) batyeshela isahlulo esikhulu soMyalezo owawuthunyelwe kubo. Kananjalo awungekhe upheze ukubhaqa inkohliso kubo, ngaphandle kwabambalwa kubo. Kodwa xolela, unge ngathi akuboni. Inene uAllâh Uyabathanda abenzi bokulungileyo"